1
00:00:07,984 --> 00:00:11,712
Hey you. You left laundry in the dryer.
Hey you. 你把衣服留在供干机里了.

2
00:00:12,537 --> 00:00:15,423
You're supposed to do the whole load yourself- start to finish.
你应该自己把这事从头至尾的全部做完.

3
00:00:16,138 --> 00:00:18,301
I forgot. I'm sorry.
我忘了. 对不起.

4
00:00:21,056 --> 00:00:25,166
So, what do you think of Dad's plans?
那么, 你对爸爸的打算怎么看?

5
00:00:26,558 --> 00:00:29,333
It's cool I guess. If he wants to do it. 
我觉得不错. 如果他希望那么做. 

6
00:00:30,139 --> 00:00:30,998
Why now?
为什么是现在?

7
00:00:32,302 --> 00:00:35,748
Well, it happens when you make a name for yourself.
Well, 一个人成名以后这些事就会发生.

8
00:00:35,900 --> 00:00:38,864
But he was just doing his job, right?
可他只是在格尽职守, 不是吗?

9
00:00:38,889 --> 00:00:39,653
Pretty funny, huh?
很有趣, huh?

10
00:00:40,147 --> 00:00:42,601
He was doing it so well, he's on the news.
他干得很好, 都上新闻了.

11
00:00:42,706 --> 00:00:43,844
Will we be no the news?
我们会上新闻吗?

12
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:48,199
Yes, I think so. at some point.
会的, 我想会的.在某个时刻.

13
00:00:48,738 --> 00:00:52,085
And some people may ask you a lot of questions.
而且有些人或许会问你许多问题.

14
00:00:52,943 --> 00:00:55,627
You have to decide for yourself whether to answer them.
你得自己决定是否回答.

15
00:00:56,949 --> 00:00:59,977
But you can always come to us and talk about it.
但是你总是可以来找我们谈谈的.

16
00:01:00,408 --> 00:01:01,710
You know that, right?
你是知道的, 对吗?

17
00:01:02,362 --> 00:01:06,522
Yeah. I just hope they don't get totally invasive.
对. 我只希望他们对我们的干扰不要太大.

18
00:01:06,541 --> 00:01:10,112
We'll keep things as normal as possible for ourselves.
我们将尽力使一切保持正常.

19
00:01:10,842 --> 00:01:12,001
At least here at home.
至少在家里.

20
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:17,189
Speaking of which, I am going to the pool tomorrow morning.
说到这个, 我明天早上打算去游泳.

21
00:01:17,335 --> 00:01:18,459
Do you want to go swimming with me?
你想和我一起去游泳吗?

22
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:21,710
Yes! Oh. What time?
好啊! Oh. 什么时候?

23
00:01:22,148 --> 00:01:26,222
Early, early, early. Oh, come on. It'll be fun.
很早, 很早, 很早. Oh, 来吧, 会很有趣的.

24
00:01:26,195 --> 00:01:28,561
We can be in the water by 7:30 in the morning.
我们可以在早晨7点半前下水.

25
00:01:28,643 --> 00:01:30,228
Mom, you're crazy.
妈妈, 你疯了.

26
00:01:30,551 --> 00:01:32,891
Don't make me go all by myself.
别让我一个人去吧.

27
00:01:32,910 --> 00:01:34,369
Leave at ten and then I'll go with you.  
10点出发我就跟你去.

28
00:01:34,427 --> 00:01:35,982
Ten! Eight o'clock.   
10点! 8点吧.

29
00:01:36,109 --> 00:01:36,701
Nine.
9点.

30
00:01:37,744 --> 00:01:39,090
Eight-thirty. Final offer. 
8点半. 不能再晚了.

31
00:01:40,636 --> 00:01:42,797
And breakfast at the Tasty Diner afterwards.
然后在Tasty Diner吃早饭.

32
00:01:43,414 --> 00:01:43,984
Deal.
一言为定.

33
00:01:44,021 --> 00:01:48,089
Good. Sleep tight.
好. 睡个好觉.

